text: Goephanes albosignatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1965.Biolib.cz - Goephanes. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Goephanes Category:Beetles described in 1965 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
